@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_qqmnbk(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.exp(((v0 + 0.08 + v1 + 0.88) / 0.25))
    tmp = tmp
    v0 = (wp.cos(wp.cos(v0 + 0.49)) / wp.abs((v2 + 0.61 - v1 + 0.06)))
    v2 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
